## Dev dependencies

# Install Node

brew install node

# Install Grunt

sudo npm install -g grunt-cli

# Install sass

sudo gem install sass

*Note: If ruby is not installed, and you're on linux machine, type: sudo apt-get install ruby1.9.1

# Install dev dependencies in package.json

npm install

*Note: This will create the folder node_modules with thre required modules for grunt to work*
